HEADWORD: Suppurate
<hw>Sup"pu*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Suppurated</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Suppurating</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>suppuratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>suppurare</ets> to suppurate, cause
