==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Suppurate
<hw>Sup"pu*rate</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cause to generate pus;
<as>as, to <ex>suppurate</ex> a sore</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Arbuthnot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

